00:38:24,590 --> 00:38:25,800
you can come to me.

857
00:38:28,670 --> 00:38:30,410
I can't betray the one I love.

858
00:38:30,960 --> 00:38:33,000
No one's asking you to betray her.

859
00:38:33,440 --> 00:38:34,680
For her,

860
00:38:34,710 --> 00:38:36,640
this might be a form of protection.

