00:38:56,960 --> 00:38:58,280
Chief Minister Pei, you called for me?

868
00:38:58,280 --> 00:38:59,280
Come look at this.

869
00:39:01,800 --> 00:39:03,030
These are finally completed

870
00:39:03,030 --> 00:39:04,230
imperial polo balls.

871
00:39:10,400 --> 00:39:11,720
Exquisitely crafted.

872
00:39:11,920 --> 00:39:13,580
Truly a treasure of the world.

873
00:39:14,840 --> 00:39:17,040
Congratulations, Chief Minister Pei.

874
00:39:17,280 --> 00:39:19,630
It's the Tang Empire
that deserves congratulations.

875
00:39:19,630 --> 00:39:20,960
Presenting such polo balls

876
00:39:20,960 --> 00:39:22,380
before foreign envoys

877
00:39:22,630 --> 00:39:24,830
befits the grandeur of our Tang Empire.

878
00:39:25,210 --> 00:39:26,380
You're right.

879
00:39:27,360 --> 00:39:28,690
There are only

880
00:39:28,960 --> 00:39:30,950
