883
00:39:36,920 --> 00:39:39,510
I'm the Minister
of the Court of State Ceremonial.

884
00:39:39,510 --> 00:39:40,670
On the day of the tournament,

885
00:39:40,670 --> 00:39:43,100
I shall perform my duties

886
00:39:43,190 --> 00:39:44,990
with full ceremonial protocol.

887
00:39:45,150 --> 00:39:46,670
Only then will foreign nations

888
00:39:46,670 --> 00:39:49,070
not dare to underestimate our Tang Empire.

889
00:39:49,670 --> 00:39:51,960
Therefore, I'm counting on you.

890
00:39:53,920 --> 00:39:56,250
Please rest assured, Chief Minister Pei.

891
00:39:58,960 --> 00:40:01,760
[Yongzhou Prefecture]

892
00:40:02,760 --> 00:40:03,620
Grand General.

893
00:40:04,230 --> 00:40:05,280
I'm here for you.

894
00:40:05,440 --> 00:40:06,900
Come with me to the palace.

895
00:40:13,030 --> 00:40:14,280
-Your Majesty.
-Your Majesty.

896
00:40:14,280 --> 00:40:15,360
The Retired Emperor

897
00:40:15,360 --> 00:40:16,400
heard about Yenisei Kirghiz spies

898
00:40:16,400 --> 00:40:17,730
infiltrating Chang'an

899
00:40:17,760 --> 00:40:19,360
and sent someone to inquire.

900
00:40:19,360 --> 00:40:21,120
How should I respond?

901
00:40:21,360 --> 00:40:23,090
The 2 spies have been executed.

902
00:40:23,400 --> 00:40:24,710
But the intelligence has already reached

903
00:40:24,710 --> 00:40:26,340
their contact, the Wolf.

904
00:40:26,630 --> 00:40:28,560
The Wolf hasn't been captured yet.

905
00:40:28,760 --> 00:40:29,670
Is that so?

906
00:40:30,190 --> 00:40:31,030
It's my fault.

907
00:40:31,670 --> 00:40:33,870
I dare not hide anything from you.

908
00:40:34,710 --> 00:40:36,240
This complicates matters.

909
00:40:36,480 --> 00:40:37,880
The Retired Emperor suggests

910
00:40:37,880 --> 00:40:39,880
that if threats are not eliminated,

911
00:40:40,000 --> 00:40:42,050
I should not attend in person.

912
00:40:42,150 --> 00:40:43,280
Your Majesty, your safety

913
00:40:43,280 --> 00:40:44,840
is of concern to the Tang Empire.

914
00:40:44,840 --> 00:40:45,480
I believe

915
00:40:45,760 --> 00:40:48,160
the Retired Emperor's concerns are valid.

916
00:40:50,400 --> 00:40:51,130
Lu Lingfeng.

917
00:40:51,670 --> 00:40:52,800
You have 2 days left.

918
00:40:52,960 --> 00:40:53,920
Are you confident

919
00:40:53,920 --> 00:40:55,150
you can capture the Wolf

920
00:40:55,150 --> 00:40:56,680
and eliminate the threats?

921
00:40:59,510 --> 00:41:00,170
No, I'm not.

922
00:41:02,550 --> 00:41:04,150
I know you've done your best.

923
00:41:04,920 --> 00:41:05,960
We'll have to proceed as is.
